data.clean_description: Indoor , best Coffeeshop quality. Strawberry Haze was created by Arjan and introduced on the market in 2006. In 2005 , Strawberry Haze won 1st prize at the Green House Very Important Smokers Panel. The buds of Strawberry Haze smell of strawberries and provide a sweet taste , which is heightened when roots are given free reign in soil. It is characterized as a tall plant with long branches. It is a simple plant to grow and maintain , as it is known to be adaptable to humidity. Flowering time is approximately 10 weeks with a THC level up to 20 and CBD of 12. This offer is for 10 gramm.
